    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in wonderful shape, ready for many more adventures! It drives like a dream and has been really well-loved, so you\u2019re getting a solid, dependable car without the 'brand new' price tag. It's perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend road trips. Come take it for a spin\u2014I just know you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 29500.0,
