      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-spec E46 M3 powered by the high-strung S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes the Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission, providing a tactile connection to the factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis dynamics are preserved through a well-maintained multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson strut front end. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced, addressing the primary mechanical concerns of this platform. While the exterior shows honest wear, the engine\u2019s volumetric efficiency and the 8,000 RPM redline remain fully intact, offering a visceral, analog performance profile.",
